[SN]TITLE[SN]
Will Instagram's new anti-bullying feature work?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Lots of people use social media every day, and bullying on social media can be a big problem.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
21 September 2016 Last updated at 07:03 BST
Now one app, Instagram, has decided to introduce a new feature to help tackle the problem.
The feature lets users pick words that they find offensive or upsetting, and block them from comments.
But will it really work? Naz has been finding out what you think.
